high_descs: Turn right then right again and face the black island on your right.
Take the knife off of the counter in front of you.
Turn around and face the counter with the tomato in front of you.
Slice the tomato in front of you.
Turn left and face the drawer to your right.
Open the drawer to your right, place the knife inside and close the drawer.
Turn right and face the counter with the tomato in front of you.
Take a tomato slice off of the counter in front of you.
Turn right then face the microwave to your left.
Heat up the tomato in the microwave then take it out and close the microwave.
Turn around and face the table in front of you.
Place the tomato slice on the table in front of you.
anns.task_desc: Place a warm tomato slice on the table.

Put the tomato slice in the microwave, start the microwave, wait, pick up the tomato slice from the microwave

Put the tomato slice on the table
